openapi: 3.0.1
components:

    Visibility:
      description: "Enumeration contains visibility status of the security element"

      x-enum-description:

        - "Colored"

      x-enum-varnames:
        - "INVISIBLE"
        - "VISIBLE"
        - "COLORED"
        - "GRAYSCALE"
        - "WHITE_IR_MATCHING"
